Fire Department

The fire department consists of a fire chief, 20 volunteer firefighters and is one of the most important institutions in Haskell. Individuals interested in joining the fire department may attend the weekly fire department exercises held each Monday night at the fire station. Our current Haskell Fire Chief is Casey Moeller.

CASEY MOELLER – FIRE CHIEF
